title: Patricia Locke Couture Bracelet in Fling
description:
A classic from Patricia's French Connection Collection, the Couture bracelet boasts an array of colorful stones, an homage to high fashion in Paris. Patricia Locke jewelry speaks a distinctive visual language that encourages self-expression, with an aura of romance and femininity.

  • Dimensions: .25 x .5 x 7.5 in.
  • Materials: antique silver plated pewter set with Swarovski crystals in boisterous Fling
